    public class OSchemaShared
extends ODocumentWrapperNoClass
implements OSchema, OCloseable, OOrientStartupListener, OOrientShutdownListener
    Shared schema class. It's shared by all the database instances that point to the same storage.

      • getClass

        public OClass getClass(String iClassName)
        Description copied from interface: OSchema
        Returns the OClass instance by class name.

        If the class is not configured and the database has an entity manager with the requested class as registered, then creates a schema class for it at the fly.

        If the database nor the entity manager have not registered class with specified name, returns null.

        Specified by:
        getClass in interface OSchema
        Parameters:
        iClassName - Name of the class to retrieve
        Returns:
        class instance or null if class with given name is not configured.

      • close

        public void close()
        Description copied from interface: OCloseable
        Closes resources inside of call of OStorage#close(). So do not use locks when you call this method or you may have deadlock during storage close. This method is completely house keeping method and plays role of Object#finalize() in case of you need to clean up resources after storage is closed.
        Specified by:
        close in interface OCloseable
